<plot>On December 24, 1972, the United States Air Force launched its largest air raid of the Viet Nam War. Christmas lost its grace in the death and destruction from the endless bombing of Vietnamese homes. Past all the chaos and havoc of war, an innocent monk who dwells in a peaceful sanctuary steps into a cold world full of hatred, deception, and death in order to break the cycle of killing.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?015997</url></doc>
